---
---

<section class="section" style="background: var(--off-white);" aria-labelledby="apart-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="apart__layout">

      <div class="apart__left reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why us</p>
        <h2 id="apart-heading">We do one thing.<br />LinkedIn.</h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
        <p class="apart__lead">
          We are not a full-service digital agency with a LinkedIn practice.
          LinkedIn is all we do. That focus is the difference.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="apart__pillars" aria-label="Our advantages">
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Specialists, not generalists</h3>
            <p>Every service we offer is built around LinkedIn. We know the algorithm, the formats, the targeting, and the content that drives results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Content that earns attention</h3>
            <p>We write for your audience, not your approval. Clear, direct B2B content that gets read and acted on.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Transparent by default</h3>
            <p>No vague reports. No hidden markups. You always know what we're doing and why.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <span class="apart__pillar-num">04</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">AI-assisted. Human-led.</h3>
            <p>We use AI to move faster and scale content production. Every output is reviewed and shaped by our team before it goes near your brand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .apart__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .apart__lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .apart__pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    padding-top: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .apart__pillar {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--sp-6) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .apart__pillar:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .apart__pillar-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 4px;
    min-width: 28px;
  }

  .apart__pillar-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .apart__pillar p {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .apart__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-10); }
  }
</style>
